HEADWORD: Archiater
<hw>Ar"chi*a`ter</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>archiatrus</ets>, Gr. <?/; pref. <?/ + <?/ physician, <?/ to
heal.]</ety> <def>Chief physician; -- a term applied, on the continent
